# clui Implementation Plan

> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.

**Goal:** Build a TUI wrapper around Claude Code (via `@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk`) with multi-session tabs, process isolation, skills management, context tools, and git worktree support.

**Architecture:** Shell + Workers model. The shell is an Ink/React TUI (main process) that renders the three-column layout and manages UI state via Zustand. Each tab spawns an isolated worker process that runs its own Claude Agent SDK instance. Shell and workers communicate over Unix Domain Sockets (JSON protocol). SQLite stores sessions, messages, pins, snapshots, and settings.

**Tech Stack:** TypeScript, Ink 6 (React 19), `@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk`, Zustand, better-sqlite3, simple-git, tsup, ink-tab, ink-scroll-view, ink-text-input

---

## File Map

```
clui/
├── package.json
├── tsconfig.json
├── tsup.config.ts
├── src/
│   ├── index.tsx                          # CLI entry — parse args, render <App>
│   ├── app.tsx                            # Root Ink component — Layout + store provider
│   │
│   ├── shared/                            # Shared between shell & workers
│   │   ├── types.ts                       # Domain types (Session, Message, Pin, Skill, etc.)
│   │   ├── ipc.ts                         # IPC message types, framing, send/receive helpers
│   │   ├── db.ts                          # SQLite init, migrations, query helpers
│   │   └── config.ts                      # Paths (db, sockets, skills dirs), defaults
│   │
│   ├── shell/                             # Main process (UI)
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   │   ├── Layout.tsx                 # Three-column flexbox grid
│   │   │   ├── TabBar.tsx                 # Session tabs + [+] button
│   │   │   ├── SessionSidebar.tsx         # Left: session history list
│   │   │   ├── SkillsSidebar.tsx          # Right: 3-tier skill browser
│   │   │   ├── ChatView.tsx               # Scrollable chat output (Static + streaming)
│   │   │   ├── ContextBar.tsx             # Active pins/skills/commands above input
│   │   │   ├── InputBar.tsx               # Text input with @file /skill parsing
│   │   │   ├── StatusBar.tsx              # Configurable status fields below input
│   │   │   ├── CompactDetail.tsx          # Expandable compact event details
│   │   │   └── WorktreePrompt.tsx         # Close-with-worktree confirmation dialog
│   │   ├── store/
│   │   │   ├── index.ts                   # Combined Zustand store
│   │   │   ├── tabs.ts                    # Tab state slice (active, list, create, close)
│   │   │   ├── sessions.ts               # Session state slice (list, colors, names)
│   │   │   ├── skills.ts                  # Skills state slice (3-tier, overrides)
│   │   │   └── settings.ts               # Settings state slice (status bar config)
│   │   └── hooks/
│   │       ├── useWorkerManager.ts        # Spawn/kill workers, IPC multiplexing
│   │       ├── useSessions.ts             # Load sessions from Claude Agent SDK
│   │       ├── useSkillDiscovery.ts       # Scan 3 skill dirs, detect overrides
│   │       └── useGit.ts                  # Branch info, diff stats via simple-git
│   │
│   ├── worker/                            # Per-tab worker process
│   │   ├── index.ts                       # Entry: connect IPC, start message loop
│   │   ├── claude-bridge.ts               # Claude Agent SDK query() wrapper
│   │   ├── context-manager.ts             # Pin resolution, snapshot, reset
│   │   └── worktree-manager.ts            # git worktree create/remove
│   │
│   └── cli/
│       └── index.ts                       # Arg parsing (--cwd, --session, --model)
│
├── db/
│   └── migrations/
│       └── 001_init.sql                   # All tables in single migration
│
└── test/
    ├── shared/
    │   ├── ipc.test.ts
    │   └── db.test.ts
    ├── worker/
    │   ├── claude-bridge.test.ts
    │   └── context-manager.test.ts
    └── shell/
        ├── store/
        │   └── tabs.test.ts
        └── components/
            └── StatusBar.test.ts
```

---

## Phase 1 — Foundation

### Task 1: Project Scaffold

**Files:**
- Create: `clui/package.json`
- Create: `clui/tsconfig.json`
- Create: `clui/tsup.config.ts`
- Create: `clui/.gitignore`

- [ ] **Step 1: Initialize project directory**

```bash
cd /Users/4thwithme/Documents/repo/clui
npm init -y
```

- [ ] **Step 2: Install dependencies**

```bash
npm install ink@6 react@19 react-dom@19 @anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk zustand better-sqlite3 simple-git ink-text-input ink-tab ink-scroll-view uuid
npm install -D typescript @types/react @types/better-sqlite3 @types/uuid tsup @types/node vitest
```

- [ ] **Step 3: Write tsconfig.json**

```json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "target": "ES2022",
    "module": "ESNext",
    "moduleResolution": "bundler",
    "jsx": "react-jsx",
    "strict": true,
    "esModuleInterop": true,
    "skipLibCheck": true,
    "outDir": "dist",
    "rootDir": "src",
    "declaration": true,
    "sourceMap": true,
    "resolveJsonModule": true,
    "forceConsistentCasingInFileNames": true,
    "types": ["node"]
  },
  "include": ["src"],
  "exclude": ["node_modules", "dist", "test"]
}
```

- [ ] **Step 4: Write tsup.config.ts**

```typescript
import { defineConfig } from "tsup";

export default defineConfig({
  entry: {
    index: "src/index.tsx",
    worker: "src/worker/index.ts",
  },
  format: ["esm"],
  target: "node20",
  platform: "node",
  splitting: false,
  sourcemap: true,
  clean: true,
  outDir: "dist",
  external: ["better-sqlite3"],
});
```

- [ ] **Step 5: Update package.json**

Add to `package.json`:

```json
{
  "type": "module",
  "bin": {
    "clui": "./dist/index.js"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "build": "tsup",
    "dev": "tsup --watch",
    "start": "node dist/index.js",
    "test": "vitest"
  }
}
```

- [ ] **Step 6: Write .gitignore**

```
node_modules/
dist/
*.db
*.db-journal
.superpowers/
```

- [ ] **Step 7: Commit**

```bash
git init
git add package.json tsconfig.json tsup.config.ts .gitignore package-lock.json
git commit -m "chore: scaffold clui project with dependencies"
```

---

### Task 2: Shared Types

**Files:**
- Create: `src/shared/types.ts`

- [ ] **Step 1: Write domain types**

```typescript
// src/shared/types.ts

export type SessionStatus = "active" | "closed" | "archived";
export type PinMode = "prompt" | "sticky";
export type PinType = "file" | "skill" | "command";
export type MessageRole = "user" | "assistant" | "system" | "tool";
export type SkillTier = "repo" | "user" | "global";

export interface Session {
  id: string;
  claudeSessionId: string | null;
  name: string;
  color: string | null;
  repoPath: string | null;
  worktreePath: string | null;
  worktreeBranch: string | null;
  model: string | null;
  totalTokens: number;
  totalCost: number;
  durationSeconds: number;
  status: SessionStatus;
  createdAt: number;
  updatedAt: number;
}

export interface Message {
  id: string;
  sessionId: string;
  role: MessageRole;
  content: string;
  tokens: number;
  cost: number;
  createdAt: number;
}

export interface Pin {
  id: string;
  sessionId: string;
  type: PinType;
  target: string;
  mode: PinMode;
  createdAt: number;
}

export interface Snapshot {
  id: string;
  sessionId: string;
  summary: string;
  contextState: string;
  filePath: string;
  createdAt: number;
}

export interface Skill {
  name: string;
  description: string;
  tier: SkillTier;
  filePath: string;
  overriddenBy: string | null; // name of higher-tier skill that overrides this
}

export interface TabState {
  id: string;
  index: number;
  sessionId: string;
  name: string;
  workerId: string | null;
  workerReady: boolean;
  worktreePath: string | null;
  worktreeBranch: string | null;
}

export interface StatusBarField {
  key: string;
  label: string;
  enabled: boolean;
}

export interface StatusBarData {
  model: string | null;
